text: Alfonso Rebochong Oiterong (October 9, 1924 - August 30, 1994)Who's who In Oceania was a politician from Palau. He was the country's Vice-President from 1981 to 1985. He was President from 2 July to 25 October 1985. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:1994 deaths Category:Presidents of Palau
